          "Hadith.4346 - Abdullah ibn Maymun narrated from Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) from his father, Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as) (peace be upon them), who said:\n\"Two units of prayer performed by a married person are better than seventy units of prayer performed by an unmarried person.\""
